caption.body: British documentary filmmaker Ellen Evans profiles Kath Holden, who reflects on her life and art in the precious world of miniatures, where her creations stand apart from the genteel museum pieces of her contemporaries.   See “Life In Miniature” by Ellen Evans in the Video Arts Gallery, located pre-security, in the International Terminal with daily operating hours of 5:00am to 10:00pm or online at: https://bit.ly/3zrlRXs
